1 依赖组件的安装
pip install flask
pip install apache_libcloud
2 运行
cd oplib/bin
python oplib.py
3 页面访问
http://x.x.x.x:8621
4 连接openstack
http://x.x.x.x:8621/connect
格式 例:
region_name:RegionOne
domain_name:domain
auth_url:http://controller:5000
project_name:admin
auth_username:admin
auth_password:000000
5 访问页面api
http://x.x.x.x:8621/v3/nova/list
http://x.x.x.x:8621/v3/image/list